{"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/SettingsSignalName\/notify","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"metadata":{"externalID":"s:3GIO18SettingsSignalNameO6notifyyA2CmF","title":"SettingsSignalName.notify","modules":[{"name":"GIO"}],"role":"symbol","roleHeading":"Case","fragments":[{"text":"case","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"notify","kind":"identifier"}],"symbolKind":"case"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The notify signal is emitted on an object when one of its properties has"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"its value set through ","type":"text"},{"code":"g_object_set_property()","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_set()"},{"text":", et al.","type":"text"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"case"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"notify","kind":"identifier"}],"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Note that getting this signal doesn’t itself guarantee that the value of","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the property has actually changed. When it is emitted is determined by the","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"derived GObject class. If the implementor did not create the property with"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"[explicit_notify](\/\/documentation\/gobject\/explicit_notify, then any call to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_set_property()"},{"type":"text","text":" results"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"in "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"notify"},{"type":"text","text":" being emitted, even if the new value is the same as the old."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"If they did pass [explicit_notify](\/\/documentation\/gobject\/explicit_notify, then this signal is emitted only"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"when they explicitly call "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_notify()"},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_notify_by_pspec()"},{"text":",","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and common practice is to do that only when the value has actually changed."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This signal is typically used to obtain change notification for a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"single property, by specifying the property name as a detail in the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_signal_connect()"},{"type":"text","text":" call, like this:"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"(C Language Example):","type":"text"}]},{"syntax":"C","code":["g_signal_connect (text_view->buffer, \"notify::paste-target-list\",","                  G_CALLBACK (gtk_text_view_target_list_notify),","                  text_view)"],"type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"It is important to note that you must use"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"#class@GObject.ParamSpec#parameter-names","isActive":true},{"text":" as","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"detail strings for the notify signal.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/gio\/settingssignalname\/notify"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"kind":"symbol","sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/SettingsSignalName"]]},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"references":{"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO":{"type":"topic","abstract":[],"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO","title":"GIO","url":"\/documentation\/gio","role":"collection","kind":"symbol"},"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/SettingsSignalName":{"navigatorTitle"